channel.title: Help with running my client
channel.description:
As I'm attempting to run my client I get this error: I never had this before:
java.io.FileNotFoundException: Cache\main_file_cache.dat (Access is denied) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.open(Native Method) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:212) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:98) at sign.signlink.run(signlink.java:58) at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:619) java.io.FileNotFoundException: Cache\main_file_cache.dat (Access is denied) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.open(Native Method) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:212) at java.io.RandomAccessFile.<init>(RandomAccessFile.java:98) at sign.signlink.run(signlink.java:58) at java.lang.Thread.run(Thread.java:619)
I accidentally made the files hidden before, but I got hem un-hidden.
Thanks, A
[br][br][size=1]Posted on: December 22, 2008, 12:40:05 pm[/size][hr]Anyone?
